usic/blackpink-seventh-anniversary-members-instagram-tributes-events-u-s-asia-3479733">继今年早些时候成立七周年后</a>，BLACKPINK 仍在与 YG Entertainment 协商续约事宜。在讨论中，说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jennie">Jennie</a>于上周（10 月 6 日）在“Born Pink”世界巡演中首演了一首特别的独奏单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/blackpink-jennie-you-and-me-3508828">“You &amp; Me”</a> 。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yg-entertainment-girl-group-babymonster-debut-november-3512212">将于 11 月出道的新 YG Entertainment 女子组合 BABYMONSTER</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
